#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/util/vtkImageExportToArray.py:7
msgid "vtkImageExportToArray - a NumPy front-end to vtkImageExport"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/util/vtkImageExportToArray.py:9
msgid ""
"This class converts a VTK image to a numpy array.  The output array will "
"always have 3 dimensions (or 4, if the image had multiple scalar components)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/util/vtkImageExportToArray.py:13
msgid ""
"To use this class, you must have numpy installed (http://numpy.scipy.org)"
msgstr ""

